ers":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"It hasn't even been five minutes. You sure you wanna stop~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":11}],"windowDisplayName":"Kokoro","body":"I like looking at the sea, but when it's right there in front of me, I gotta get closer to it! Ah! I just saw a fish jump out of the water!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":11,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":11,"voiceId":"event155-03-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"And off she goes.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Kokoro-chan sure has a lot of energy~. I guess she couldn't pick up on these youthful vibes here~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Oh well, everyone has their own way of enjoying themselves~... Mmm, cream buns taste so good when you eat them while looking at the sea~♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"Aoba-san, you always do your own thing, don't you? No matter where you are, you're very laid-back...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event155-03-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Yeah~, that's just how I am~. Want one? These cream buns are mighty tasty~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"No... I'm fine.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event155-03-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... I've been extremely busy with the archery club and band practice lately... so maybe it's good to take a break like this and just relax sometimes.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event155-03-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"True, true~. It's not good to push yourself too hard~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Oh, yeah~. Looking at the sea reminded me of something. Are there any old train tracks or stations that aren't in use anymore around here~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... Yes. If you walk south along the coast, I'm pretty sure there are...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event155-03-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Then let's go there~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"There was a picture of something like that in the photo book with the sunflower field.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"I was thinking that the sunflowers could be somewhere near there~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event155-03-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"... That's quite the deduction you've made. L